# Lab 6D – systemd Hardening

1. Edit service override
   systemctl edit daemon-workload.service

2. Add the following security directives:

   [Service]

   # Process & Privilege Controls
   NoNewPrivileges=yes

   # Filesystem Protections
   ProtectSystem=full
   ProtectHome=yes
   PrivateTmp=yes

   # Resource Limits
   MemoryMax=100M
   CPUQuota=50%

3. Reload systemd
   systemctl daemon-reload

4. Restart service
   systemctl restart daemon-workload.service

5. Verify protections
   systemctl show daemon-workload.service | grep -E 'MemoryMax|CPUQuota|NoNewPrivileges'
